name: ChallengeBox Boxing Fitness
summary:
Workout with friends 1vs1.

Variety of workouts to 1vs1:
1. 🥊 Boxing Challenge 
2. ⚒️ Rock Crusher Challenge
3. 🎶 Lane Leap Challenge 

🥊 Boxing:
A Full body boxing workout, makes you burn ~200 calories in less than 20 mins. 

⚒️ Rock Crusher:
Break as many as rocks you can in 1 min with hammers in both hands.
It's a great STRESS BUSTER 💆‍♂️. 

🎶 Lane Leap:
Dodge the blocks, across lanes. 
Great for LEGS 🦵 and Core \͝(‡)͝/
